name: Fighter Being
description:
Fighter Being
Where there is magic, treasures, secrets, there should be battles too. To win a battle you need a party and that party needs a Fighter to stay in front. This Blue Fighter Being is your front line and he trusts beings of the color Blue!

As a <blue> being it can combine powers with other <blue> beings. If the blue beings win a fight - they get the loot drop for free.


Character from a live performance from Fireter - a theater of shadow and fire. 

Also a <blue> <fighter> 
Original NFT from
www.fireter.com
